==English==

===Etymology===
From [[cripple]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]

===Noun===
'''crippleware'''

#{{cattag|Internet}} A program whose functionality is severely limited beyond that of [[shareware]], often in the interest of its author having the user make complete purchase of the un-crippled version.

